{"id": 2731, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些线上的“断舍离”做法？", "description": "确定要彻底清除吗？确定。（题图来自：iStock ©️nuvolanevicata ）", "record_count": 4445, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190113213049lkU7XIGHBACPsjRW.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-18T03:00:50Z", "options": [{"id": 333056, "content": "清空消息通知", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 323584, "content": "微信爱删好友算么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557343}, {"id": 324098, "content": "懒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148667}, {"id": 323591, "content": "一些照片会定期清理，不会留存", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563559}, {"id": 323340, "content": "删除所有朋友圈/微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023014}, {"id": 323341, "content": "容易浪费时间沉迷的app就直接卸载，等真正需要的时候再下载回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 192, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561341}, {"id": 323342, "content": "屏蔽关于“蔡徐坤、王俊凯、王源、易烊千玺、吴亦凡...”的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 432, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 323343, "content": "清空缓存垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 323344, "content": "能不注册的软件尽量不注册，能浏览的内容，尽量不留言", "image": null, "praise_count": 485, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599749}, {"id": 323345, "content": "不玩手机、电脑就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501511}, {"id": 323346, "content": "每完成一个任务，就会把电脑屏幕上的所有相关文件全部归档保存，然后从屏幕上删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 220, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561346}, {"id": 323347, "content": "手机里关闭所有非必需的app通知。", "image": null, "praise_count": 838, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374094}, {"id": 323348, "content": "社交软件除了微信QQ就只留下一个，删掉就不会再下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419410}, {"id": 323349, "content": "收进群聊助手且不提醒。/微信勿扰模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374094}, {"id": 323350, "content": "定期杀毒清理垃圾。还有就是玩太久某一局通不过的游戏直接删除。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428289}, {"id": 323351, "content": "感觉任何应用不合适就立马删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 264, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 323353, "content": "上个月份没有对话的聊天，直接删除对话窗", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 323354, "content": "本地歌曲听到一个月左右会清理一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552224}, {"id": 323355, "content": "安装新软件要求通知权限果断点“不允许”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 381, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847412}, {"id": 323867, "content": "主动断网一天", "image": "img/option/option/201901221618112Q3sPZdjlKUCna8O.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564773}, {"id": 323356, "content": "删游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988119}, {"id": 323357, "content": "屏蔽关于“蔡徐坤、王俊凯、王源、易烊千玺、吴亦凡..,,.”的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149680}, {"id": 323358, "content": "没有聊过天的或是很久没聊过也再也不会聊天的好友直接删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561389}, {"id": 324641, "content": "关闭通知", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567417}, {"id": 323362, "content": "关闭朋友圈（开始自闭）", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522644}, {"id": 323875, "content": "删了所有没用软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564780}, {"id": 324643, "content": "关闭弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567417}, {"id": 323364, "content": "点赞就好，不回复这个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353851}, {"id": 323365, "content": "除了微信，短信，其他app全都关闭通知，横幅，小红点", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 323366, "content": "系统自带的软件一般都保留，体量小，无广告，功能够用就是最棒了。\n同功能软件 择优只留下一个。\n可以用小程序替代的绝不留下app。\n所有不能替代又有点讨厌的（支付宝，大都会）全部隐藏到看不见的最下层，使用时点捷径就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940887}, {"id": 323367, "content": "戒掉手机。。。。骗你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 323368, "content": "不定期把照片上传备份后 删掉照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561452}, {"id": 323369, "content": "删掉所有可能暴露隐私的动态", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201284}, {"id": 323373, "content": "每天清理手机里的垃圾图片跟截图，把记录习惯app上的待做项全部确认做过", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508497}, {"id": 323375, "content": "超过一个月不用的APP一定删掉，哪怕下次需要再下载，以及定时清理信息内存和好友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397575}, {"id": 323377, "content": "没有特别的剧要追时，删掉视频APP。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329621}, {"id": 323378, "content": "能用小程序的尽量不下载app", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720470}, {"id": 323423, "content": "一天清理一次手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 323424, "content": "通过对比消除太正常了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367725}, {"id": 323425, "content": "关闭微信朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513367}, {"id": 323426, "content": "這有什麼值得討論的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518401}, {"id": 323427, "content": "微信去年一年应该点赞5个左右，用了6年微信，一条朋友圈还是为了证明自己没有关闭朋友圈发的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597047}, {"id": 323429, "content": "定期将手机恢复出厂设置", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512805}, {"id": 323430, "content": "手机app图标太丑到底删还是不删？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351826}, {"id": 323432, "content": "关闭朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468876}, {"id": 323433, "content": "定期清楚不必要的收藏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 323443, "content": "我在考虑卸载b站（反正电脑上能看也不在乎手机上多一个）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396508}, {"id": 323444, "content": "每次使用完一个不常用APP 会从运行程序里清除 避免占用运行内存", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559203}, {"id": 323445, "content": "清理购物车  一遍又一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232947}, {"id": 328054, "content": "关闭后台通知", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587459}]}